{"story":{"group_1":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3053_00_01","textHome":"啊，好呀，我叫牧野郁美。@虽说是魔法少女，不过我已经19岁高中毕业了，@平常是女仆咖啡厅……@啊！郁、郁美是能歌善舞的女仆长哦！@我会满怀爱意，让大家都迷上我哦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":100}]}],"group_10":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3053_00_17","textHome":"郁美知道，就算是喊我阿姨还有老太婆，@也都是大家爱我的表现吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":305300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":305300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":100}]}],"group_11":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3053_00_18","textHome":"郁美绝对不会改变！@因为现在的郁美并不只是自己一个人的，@还包含着挚友满满的心愿！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":100}]}],"group_12":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3053_00_19","textHome":"郁美的爱越来越大，已经快要溢出来了哦！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":300}]}],"group_13":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3053_00_20","textHome":"如果我不能活下来，就如同我杀了她一样。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":305300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":305300,"motion":0}]}],"group_14":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3053_00_21","textHome":"私生活还有魔法少女，@虽然很辛苦，但我绝对不会忘记笑容。@这就是我作为专业的决心。@因为我是女仆郁美。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305300}]}],"group_15":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3053_00_22","textHome":"不管如何努力，@只靠自己的力量没有办法避免魔法少女的宿命。@所以，我走上了这条他人铺好的道路。@不过，我想要到达的终点一定是存在的。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":305300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":305300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":305300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":305300}]}],"group_16":[{"autoTurnFirst":6.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3053_00_23","textHome":"我想要再一次，@自己去开辟一条逃离魔法少女宿命的道路。@这已经不只是是荆棘之路了。@这是被带刺的铁丝网所包围的血腥之路。@即便如此，我也已经做好了觉悟。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"eyeClose":1,"id":305300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":305300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":305300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":0}]}],"group_17":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3053_00_24","textHome":"欢迎回来，主人！@今天也过来看郁美，郁美真的好开心！@今天一天就悠闲的享受吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.3,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":400}]}],"group_18":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3053_00_25","textHome":"现在赶到车站的话……@舞蹈课就快要赶不上了……啊！@嗯呜呜，郁美要迟到了……嘤嘤嘤……@被骗了吗？"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":300,"tear":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"id":305300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":305300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":305300,"tear":0}]}],"group_19":[{"autoTurnFirst":1.4,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":200,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3053_00_26","textHome":"变好吃吧，变好吃吧，@好了，郁美特制的美味午饭套餐做好啦！@快趁热吃吧♪"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":100}]}],"group_2":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.4,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3053_00_02","textHome":"大家的偶像，牧野郁美，就是“郁美”哦！@今天开始就会让你变得脑子里只想着郁美，@做好觉悟吧！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":400}]}],"group_20":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.8,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3053_00_27","textHome":"各位放学回来还有下班回家的主人和大小姐们，@我有重大消息要公布哦！@从现在起，@郁美的飘然心动演唱会就要开始啦——♪"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":305300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":305300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":400}]}],"group_21":[{"autoTurnFirst":5.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":0,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3053_00_28","textHome":"哈啊……@前辈在的时候还能一起做营业结束后的工作，@今天只有我一个……郁美好寂寞。@呜诶诶……哎，去算账吧……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.2,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"eyeClose":1,"id":305300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":305300,"motion":100,"tear":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":0,"tear":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":305300}]}],"group_22":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3053_00_29","textHome":"这才不是人设呢。@现在你们看到的我，就是真实的郁美哦♪@之前的你们见到的一定都是幻想，都是幽灵！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"id":305300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":0}]}],"group_23":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":2,"eyeClose":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"tear":1,"voice":"vo_char_3053_00_30","textHome":"呜诶诶诶，附近竟然有魔女，郁美好害怕啊！@有谁、有谁能帮帮我吗！@诶……一个人都不在……@还是先打倒它再说吧……"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"id":305300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":0.1,"chara":[{"eyeClose":0,"id":305300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":305300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":400}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"id":305300,"motion":0}]}],"group_24":[{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":100,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3053_00_31","textHome":"无尽镜界里要是有很多郁美的复制的话，@那镜界里一定会充满粉色，变得超级可爱！@怎么办呢～♪"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":305300,"motion":400}]}],"group_25":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.9,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3053_00_32","textHome":"哇啊，谢谢大家，有那么多人为了郁美而来～@♪诶，搞错了吗!?现在要和大家一起战斗@吗，怎么会这样！"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.8,"chara":[{"id":305300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":305300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"id":305300,"motion":300}]}],"group_26":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3053_00_33","textHome":"现在虽然在从事女仆的工作，但郁美的梦想，@是用郁美的魅力把大家统统萌倒，@成为一个出色的偶像。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.2,"chara":[{"id":305300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":4.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305300}]}],"group_27":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.2,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":400,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3053_00_34","textHome":"诶，郁美在发呆吗？@不对哦，才不会呢！@笑容和活力就是郁美的魅力。@大家一起欢笑吧♪"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":2.7,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":200}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305300}]}],"group_28":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":300,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3053_00_35","textHome":"郁美最～喜欢粉色的，轻飘飘的衣服了。@因为可爱又轻飘飘的东西，@就会让人感到幸福吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305300}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.0,"chara":[{"id":305300,"motion":1}]},{"autoTurnFirst":5.0,"chara":[{"id":305300,"motion":400}]}],"group_29":[{"autoTurnFirst":3.6,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"eyeClose":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":1,"pos":1,"voice":"vo_char_3053_00_36","textHome":"哇，这件衣服好可爱♪@对了，穿上它和新菜单一起发到SNS上，@粉丝一定也会很开心吧。"}]},{"autoTurnFirst":1.5,"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":0}]},{"autoTurnFirst":3.5,"chara":[{"id":305300,"motion":100}]},{"autoTurnFirst":6.0,"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":305300,"motion":400}]}],"group_3":[{"autoTurnFirst":2.0,"c